   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Transform Children&apos;s Lives Through Hip Hop Therapy</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We believe that music is the glue that connects us all--we are all healed and transformed by music. Since 2004, Beats Rhymes and Life, BRL, has been using Hip Hop Therapy to address trauma among urban youth. Youth living in urban environments experience traumatic stress at rates higher than soldiers returning from combat. But unlike soldiers, children in the inner city never leave the combat zone. We need your help to offer Hip Hop Therapy to 150 youth.</narrative>
  </description>
